* Monitors
  See https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Monitors/
  @code conf
  monitor=DP-1,2560x1440@144,0x0,1
  @end

  See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Keywords/}[The Keywords wiki page] for more

  Execute your favorite apps at launch
  @code conf
  exec-once = waybar & hyprpaper & firefox
  @end

* Source a file (multi-file configs)
  `source = ~/.config/hypr/myColors.conf`

* Set programs that you use
  @code conf
  $terminal = kitty
  $fileManager = dolphin
  $menu = wofi --show drun
  @end

* Some default env vars.
  @code conf
  env = XCURSOR_SIZE,24
  env = QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME,qt5ct # change to qt6ct if you have that
  @end
* NVIDIA Stuff
  @code conf
  env = LIBVA_DRIVER_NAME,nvidia
  env = XDG_SESSION_TYPE,wayland
  env = __GLX_VENDOR_LIBRARY_NAME,nvidia
  env = WLR_NO_HARDWARE_CURSORS,1
  @end

* Categories
  For all categories, see {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Variables/}[the Variables wiki page]
** Input
   @code conf
   input {
   kb_layout = us
   kb_variant =
   kb_model =
   kb_options =
   kb_rules =

   follow_mouse = 1

   touchpad {
   natural_scroll = no
   }

   sensitivity = 0 # -1.0 - 1.0, 0 means no modification.
   }
   @end
** General config
   See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Variables/}[Variables wiki page] for more
   Please see {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Tearing/}[Tearing wiki entry] before you turn `allow_tearing` on
   @code conf
   general {

   gaps_in = 5
   gaps_out = 20
   border_size = 2
   col.active_border = rgba(33ccffee) rgba(00ff99ee) 45deg
   col.inactive_border = rgba(595959aa)

   layout = dwindle

   allow_tearing = false
   }
   @end
** Decorations
   See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Variables/}[Variables] for more options and explanations on decoration config
   Some default animations, see {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Animations/}[The animations wiki page] for more
   See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Master-Layout/}[Master Layout] for more options
   @code conf
   decoration {

   rounding = 10

   blur {
   enabled = true
   size = 3
   passes = 1
   }

   drop_shadow = yes
   shadow_range = 4
   shadow_render_power = 3
   col.shadow = rgba(1a1a1aee)
   }
   @end
** Animations
   See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Animations/}[The animations wiki page] for more
   @code conf
   animations {
   enabled = yes


   bezier = myBezier, 0.05, 0.9, 0.1, 1.05

   animation = windows, 1, 7, myBezier
   animation = windowsOut, 1, 7, default, popin 80%
   animation = border, 1, 10, default
   animation = borderangle, 1, 8, default
   animation = fade, 1, 7, default
   animation = workspaces, 1, 6, default
   }
   @end
** Dwindle layout
   See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Dwindle-Layout/}[The Dwindle Layout wiki page] for more
   master switch for pseudotiling. Enabling is bound to mainMod + P in the keybinds section below
   @code conf
   dwindle {
   pseudotile = yes 
   preserve_split = yes
   }
   @end
** Master layout
   see {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Master-Layout/}[The Master Layout wiki page] for more
   @code conf
   master {
   new_is_master = true
   }
   @end
** Misc
   See {https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Variables/}[Variables] for more options and explanations on decoration config
   @code conf
   gestures {
   workspace_swipe = off
   }

   misc {
   force_default_wallpaper = -1 # Set to 0 or 1 to disable the anime mascot wallpapers
   }
   @end

